{"tid":1379140,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[小小整合] 想搵堆post告戒下大家","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T19:21:52.000Z","uid":289578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bb64012c2a7a9d4662baaea46a7c7474b86da2","tid":1379140,"uid":289578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"人在海外留學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日有班人聽到有人讀獨立宣言就屌哂鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係革命呀  Zero-sum game 零和遊戲嚟架 只有一邊嬴一邊輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論邊個結局 只要有共鏟黨控制嘅成份 佢都唔會俾你好過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以我希望可以潜移默化 要製造機會 而唔係等機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整一個可行, 有效嘅憲法同政府出嚟 說服香港人係可以揀自己嘅未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>告誡post</strong><br />\n[超突發] 運動出現重大突破 有望九月前爭取成果<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377328\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377328</a><br />\n[緊急] 你知唔知，場運動就快輸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378617\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378617</a><br />\n今日香港同1989年「六四」愈來愈似，就係差1989年6月3日一件最關鍵嘅事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378426\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378426</a><br />\n【運動蜜月期正式完結】請大家唔好再戇鳩 講乜野林鄭好驚、共產黨好驚...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377339\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377339</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>建議post</strong><br />\n經歷左呢幾次，終於發現運動個樽頸係邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1377979\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1377979</a><br />\n[前線心態調整] 我係勇武，我覺得衝，都要目標導向，Objective-Oriented<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378355\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378355</a><br />\n<br />\n最後想招人入Discord Server組香城ONLINE公會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"